title: "HIV Drug Resistance Prediction with ESM-2 Protein Language Model"
version: 1.0.1
date-released: 2026-05-17
url: "https://github.com/hayden-farquhar/HIV-ESM-2"
repository-code: "https://github.com/hayden-farquhar/HIV-ESM-2"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - HIV drug resistance
  - protein language models
  - ESM-2
  - antiretroviral therapy
  - machine learning
  - drug resistance mutations
abstract: >-
  A machine learning pipeline for predicting HIV drug resistance from
  protein sequences using ESM-2 protein language model embeddings. The
  attention-weighted pooling approach achieves 0.968 mean AUC across
  18 antiretroviral drugs, with 2.48x enrichment for known drug resistance
  mutations in high-attention positions.
